title: Antonio Brown trades, OBJ rumors, AAF picks with Sean Wagner (Football 2/15)
description:
Will Brinson and Sean Wagner-McGough break down the latest news and notes around the NFL, including the Bengals being unable to find a defensive coordinator, the NFL's combine situation and Pierre Garcon being cut. Then the guys discuss some airplane etiquette (25:00) and talk about where Antonio  Brown could land (33:00), Odell Beckham trade rumors and pick a team for Sean to root for in the AAF.
